item.title: Go-LeetCode
item.description: Roman To Integer Roman numerals are represented by seven different symbols: I , V , X , L , C , D and M . Symbol Value I 1 V 5 X 10 L 50 C 100 D 500 M 1000 For example, two is written as II in Roman numeral, just two one’s added together.
